                "text": "Once per day as a move action, an oma can sing a telepathic song that either encourages its friends or dispirits its foes. The oma can grant a +2 morale bonus to ability checks, attack rolls, and skill checks to all allies within 60 feet. Alternatively, the oma can cause all enemies within 60 feet who fail DC 24 Will saving throws to take a \u20132 penalty to ability checks, attack rolls, and skill checks. This bonus or penalty lasts for 8 rounds.",
